## collect variable

Pops TOS (a number) and then forms a tuple of the top `n` remaining values and pushes it as new TOS. The original collected stack values are removed from d-stack.

( ... n \-\-\- ... \[...\] )

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
collect: (ctx: StackContext) => StackContext
```
